{"tid":664552,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[求屌醒]好多負能量","createTime":"2018-05-14T07:24:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T13:10:31.000Z","uid":119349,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"be69411be811aa93ed7053665c4908192d83222b","tid":664552,"uid":119349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:24:52.000Z","msg":"個人好重負能量，發現現實生活好似無人著緊我咁，開始變得「佛系」，對感情，學業都唔想理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開始不斷打機、訓覺去逃避個世界<br />\n<br />\n其實自己知好多人著緊我、好多朋友，早d溫書會考高分d。<br />\n但係就係覺得人地唔係真心對自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，俾打機迷住搞到d嘢一拖再拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知係自己衰，自己冇用。跪求巴絲屌醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底點先走得返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6628f3ca88e9cf6a790711b9cb164893fbc2ee02","tid":664552,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:26:46.000Z","msg":"\\<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/"},{"pid":"149c7c73a2bf95537228cfad448939cfafdb1f39","tid":664552,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6628f3ca88e9cf6a790711b9cb164893fbc2ee02","tid":664552,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:26:46.000Z","msg":"\\<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:31:51.000Z","msg":"腸"},{"pid":"4091e9688d610f4eecd09a27653db3ae0934e4d7","tid":664552,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"149c7c73a2bf95537228cfad448939cfafdb1f39","tid":664552,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6628f3ca88e9cf6a790711b9cb164893fbc2ee02","tid":664552,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:26:46.000Z","msg":"\\<img src=\"/assets/fa